new Saint M829 pedals is just 397g, a full 156g lighter than the bulky current M828 Saints. Shimano says they will ship with both 3mm &amp; 6mm pin sets, and the pedals are installed with a 8mm hex (no external wrench flats.)</p><h3>New lightweight Shimano XT alloy flat pedals</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30102418/Shimano-lightweight-XT-gravity-enduro-freeride-DH-mountain-bike-platform-pedals_M8141-angled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30102418/Shimano-lightweight-XT-gravity-enduro-freeride-DH-mountain-bike-platform-pedals_M8141-angled.jpg\" alt=\"Shimano lightweight XT gravity enduro freeride DH mountain bike platform pedals, PD-M8141&nbsp;angled\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30102418/Shimano-lightweight-XT-gravity-enduro-freeride-DH-mountain-bike-platform-pedals_M8141-angled.jpg 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30102418/Shimano-lightweight-XT-gravity-enduro-freeride-DH-mountain-bike-platform-pedals_M8141-angled-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30102418/Shimano-lightweight-XT-gravity-enduro-freeride-DH-mountain-bike-platform-pedals_M8141-angled-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30102418/Shimano-lightweight-XT-gravity-enduro-freeride-DH-mountain-bike-platform-pedals_M8141-angled-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30102418/Shimano-lightweight-XT-gravity-enduro-freeride-DH-mountain-bike-platform-pedals_M8141-angled-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploa